column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,f.peak, f.integr, f.rms,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN FIRST AS f ON f.objid = s.bestobjid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #
